810
00:44:10,589 --> 00:44:11,660
Apa?

811
00:44:11,859 --> 00:44:14,589
Aku mengkhawatirkan Da Bin.

812
00:44:15,160 --> 00:44:18,560
Kamu harus mengandalkan suamimu.

813
00:44:18,629 --> 00:44:21,200
Kyung Jin, ayolah.

814
00:44:24,170 --> 00:44:25,940
Mungkin aku harus mengasuh Da Bin saja.

815
00:44:25,999 --> 00:44:28,440
Ayolah. Sekali ini saja.

816
00:44:28,540 --> 00:44:30,339
Lakukan untukku sekali ini saja.

817
00:44:50,959 --> 00:44:52,229
Ayo.

818
00:44:53,160 --> 00:44:55,869
Da Bin, ini topeng emas.

819
00:44:59,640 --> 00:45:03,109
Baik, sekali lagi. Kali ini bersama.

820
00:45:03,780 --> 00:45:04,810
Satu.

821
00:45:07,180 --> 00:45:08,550
Lihat ayah.

822
00:45:08,609 --> 00:45:11,320
Putri ayah seperti model.

823
00:45:14,790 --> 00:45:17,060
Ini dia.

824
00:45:40,140 --> 00:45:41,650
Bu Park,

825
00:45:41,709 --> 00:45:44,180
