Pak Bang.

907
00:49:37,879 --> 00:49:38,879
Pak Kim.

908
00:49:40,349 --> 00:49:42,420
Tolong jujur kepadaku.

909
00:49:43,420 --> 00:49:44,489
Mi Hye.

910
00:49:45,459 --> 00:49:46,660
Apa kamu sungguh menyukainya?

911
00:49:47,430 --> 00:49:50,800
Tidak. Woo Jin tidak menganggapnya begitu.

912
00:49:51,430 --> 00:49:53,759
Berapa kali harus kubilang kamu salah?

913
00:49:53,969 --> 00:49:56,129
Woo Jin, bicaralah agar kita bisa mengakhiri ini.

914
00:49:57,940 --> 00:49:58,999
Kurasa

915
00:49:59,969 --> 00:50:01,109
aku menyukainya.

916
00:50:02,140 --> 00:50:03,140
Apa?

917
00:50:04,810 --> 00:50:05,839
Ya.

918
00:50:06,709 --> 00:50:10,109
Memang benar aku menyukai Nona Kang.

919
00:50:10,209 --> 00:50:11,249
Woo Jin.

920
00:50:11,320 --> 00:50:12,349
Apa?

921
00:50:13,989 --> 00:50:15,249
